subject: logging_service: Add device level logging for Chassis
commitMessage:
logging_service: Add device level logging for Chassis

Support features like AutoExpand, canDelegateTop, and canDelegateSkip.

Chassis  level logs for all resources that is contained by the current
chassis. This may include Drives, Processors, and others.

The log services are based off a Chassis resource. The logs entries can
be linked by the devices related to the chassis.

The log entries will be created by object paths in the form of
`/xyz/openbmc_project/logging/devices/${CHASSIS}/${DEVICE}/${ENTRY}`.

This will allow the Chassis log service to contain logs for different
devices. This will be handle at each devices' handler. The log service
will simply pull the name from the d-bus path.

For example,

Chassis
```
/xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/board_0
|__/xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/board_0/drive_0
|__/xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/board_0/cpu_0
```

Log Entries
```
/xyz/openbmc_project/logging/devices/board_0/drive_0/entry0
/xyz/openbmc_project/logging/devices/board_0/drive_0/entry1
/xyz/openbmc_project/logging/devices/board_0/cpu_0/entry0
/xyz/openbmc_project/logging/devices/board_0/cpu_0/entry1
...
```

Tested:
Passed Redfish Validator
```
*** /redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/
         Type (#LogServiceCollection.LogServiceCollection), GET SUCCESS (time: 0.0208)
         PASS
URI acquired ends in slash: /redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/DeviceLog/

*** /redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/DeviceLog/
/redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/DeviceLog/ @odata.id: Expected @odata.id to match URI link /redfish/v1/Systems/system/LogServices/board_0
         Type (#LogService.v1_1_0.LogService), GET SUCCESS (time: 0.019991)
         PASS

*** /redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/DeviceLog/Entries
/redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/DeviceLog/Entries @odata.id: Expected @odata.id to match URI link /redfish/v1/Systems/test/LogServices/board_0/Entries
         Type (#LogEntryCollection.LogEntryCollection), GET SUCCESS (time: 0.021477)
         PASS

*** /redfish/v1/Chassis/board_0/LogServices/DeviceLog/Entries/log0
         Type (#LogEntry.v1_7_0.LogEntry), GET SUCCESS (time: 0.023346)
         PASS
```
